---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="页面未找到">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 text-center">
    <div class="font-[var(--font-pixel)] text-6xl mb-8">404</div>

    <div class="mb-8">
      <pre class="inline-block text-left text-xs leading-tight text-[var(--color-text-light)]">
{`  ╔══════════════════╗
  ║  ░░░░░░░░░░░░░░  ║
  ║  ░░ 404 NOT ░░░  ║
  ║  ░░  FOUND  ░░░  ║
  ║  ░░░░░░░░░░░░░░  ║
  ╚══════════════════╝`}
      </pre>
    </div>

    <p class="text-[var(--color-text-light)] mb-8">
      你好像走丢了…这个页面不存在 ✦
    </p>

    <div class="flex justify-center gap-4">
      <a href="/" class="pixel-btn bg-[var(--color-accent)] text-white">回首页</a>
      <a href="/blog" class="pixel-btn bg-[var(--color-bg-card)]">看博客</a>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 text-xs text-[var(--color-text-light)]">
      <p>TIP: 检查一下 URL 是否正确</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
